###

### atac - 1000 LI vs oras gol, astept 0 pierderi
### (1000/40000)^1.5 = 0 pierderi, resurse furate = carry*1000/3
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cities/{{cityIdAtk}}/commands
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAtk}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ATTACK",
  "targetCityId": "{{cityIdDef}}",
  "units": { "LIGHT_INFANTRY": 100 }
}

###

### atac - 1000 LI vs 1000 ATI
### astept: ~770 LI supravietuiesc (23% pierderi), toti ATI mor
### (15000/40000)^1.5 = 0.229
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cities/{{cityIdAtk}}/commands
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAtk}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ATTACK",
  "targetCityId": "{{cityIdDef}}",
  "units": { "LIGHT_INFANTRY": 1000 }
}

